Once you look at it, the whole picture is clear now. Israel has been doing everything leading up to this for decades. All the manipulations of American politics, Democrats and Republicans alike, all the manipulations of the media and banking system, including dividing America racially and the creation of identity politics....all to siphon wealth for power over the US, from the inside, all so they can conquer their surrounding areas, to weaken and ethnically cleanse it of all others, and in doing so, they also effectively conquered the US in a way too.  

Make no mistake, Israel may try to paint themselves as the good guys, but this is purely a religious war of revenge. It's a proverbial jihad. Just a continuation of the war that has been waging between Jews and Muslims for thousands of years, the only difference is one side wears western suits while the other side wears hijabs. Both sides are assholes, both sides are America's enemy. Israel is just trying to once and for all lay claim to what it considers its holy land, and this is ultimately nothing more than a holy war, thousands of years in the making, or a century in the making, depending on how you look at it. 

America should take no part in it, because even if Israel ultimately wins, it will still have all that power it has exerted in the US, which it won't let go, it will simply abuse it out of boredom, because the purpose of taking all that power in the first place will be fulfilled, but that doesn't mean the power no longer serves a purpose to them, they will just create a new purpose for it. America need to be free from foreign influence, otherwise we are no different than slaves on a plantation. 

This is why Trump must break the wheel that constantly turns and crushes people under it. ALL foreign influence in America is inherently bad for America. No foreign influence in America will ever be good for America. No foreign country will support making America great, unless they intend to exploit that greatness to their own ends, which is exactly why such games cannot be allowed to be played in the first place anymore. We can't MAGA with the Israel lobby controlling American interests, any MAGA under such a system would ultimately be fleeting, as it would only exist to be controlled to serve Israel's purposes.
